---
title: Ultimate Creamy Burrata, Truffle and Mushroom Risotto with Crispy Serrano Ham and Garlic Ciabatta
description: Looking for a taste of everyday luxury? This Ultimate Creamy Burrata, Truffle and Mushroom Risotto is our best ever version, with premium ingredients for an extra special twist on a classic recipe.

Translated from the Italian for ‘buttery’, burrata is a fresh and creamy cheese that is perfect for sharing. Typical of the Puglia region, burrata consists of a casing of mozzarella with filled with soft stracciatella and clotted cream. Perfect for adding to salads, pizzas and pasta or as an appetiser.
